Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.40,0:00:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（明明老公就在一旁）\N（却无法停止外遇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.00,0:00:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（在心跳加速的状况下）\N（点燃欲火的欲求不满妻）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.60,0:00:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（直到中出之前决不放开）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（千沙，27岁，结婚第3年）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.06,0:00:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.66,0:00:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.53,0:00:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束后就会马上回来\N一定要马上回来哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.40,0:00:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.60,0:00:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要煮好热热的味噌汤哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.73,0:00:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要煮好哦\N知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.26,0:00:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.80,0:00:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那走咯\N要走了?还很早啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.06,0:00:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要是临时有事就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.06,0:00:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以还是早点过去才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.46,0:00:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么吧\N再来亲嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.73,0:01:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲一个嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.66,0:01:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好寂寞啊\N我很快就会回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.93,0:01:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你是大夜啊\N我晚上就只有自己一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.60,0:01:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你睡觉就好了啊 ，不想睡吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.60,0:01:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.80,0:01:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得有精神了，可是我得...\N不要啦，一会就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.86,0:01:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下就好吗?怎么办?\N好嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.53,0:01:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞\N这会受不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.00,0:01:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间还很早嘛，我会很寂寞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.20,0:02:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很寂寞啊，可是得去工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.13,0:02:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经好有活力了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.13,0:02:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以舔吗?\N只是稍微的话可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.66,0:02:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.00,0:02:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.46,0:03:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了\N不行啦，不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.06,0:03:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一点吧\N再一点？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.73,0:04:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何?\N好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.20,0:05:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.26,0:05:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.93,0:06:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好浓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得走了\N抱歉咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.73,0:06:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快迟到了，那我走咯\N慢走哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.93,0:06:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出门咯\N满走，路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.93,0:06:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.46,0:06:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来，辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿哒哒的\N是啊，都湿透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.06,0:07:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下大雨呢\N还好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.53,0:07:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷啊\N还好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.73,0:07:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了放伞进去呢\N真是抱歉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去洗澡\N是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.33,0:07:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我拿毛巾吧，不快洗会感冒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.86,0:07:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吗?\N没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.13,0:07:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛巾就麻烦你了\N知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.26,0:07:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?\N觉得有点畏寒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.93,0:07:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧?\N变得有点发烧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.13,0:07:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.06,0:07:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不是没事呢\N这样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.20,0:08:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快睡吧\N是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.20,0:08:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点想睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再麻烦你咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.93,0:08:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会传染的\N放心，不会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.40,0:08:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快休息吧\N那我去睡咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.53,0:08:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.20,0:08:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗?\N我老公身体不舒服，正在睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在?\N不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.93,0:08:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说他今天上大夜?\N是没错啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.80,0:09:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是一直好想做，你摸摸看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.46,0:09:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这个样子了\N是没错啦，但老公正在睡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.66,0:09:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天就...\N怎么在睡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.93,0:09:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他感冒了\N真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.20,0:09:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在想做得受不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.20,0:09:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我整个就快要爆了\N我老公在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.46,0:09:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啦\N不然去老公旁边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.06,0:09:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能，而且不知道何时会醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.80,0:09:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经受不了了啊\N安静就好吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.33,0:10:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静也不行啦\N可以的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.13,0:10:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.73,0:10:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是喜欢我这根?\N是没错啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.33,0:10:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想要的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.06,0:10:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么啊?\N拜托你，今天就回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.46,0:10:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是期待到都没自慰\N就来搞一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.93,0:10:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被发现的话\N没事的 安静就行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来亲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.40,0:11:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.73,0:11:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我回去却硬了起来啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.20,0:11:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想做吧?奶头都好有活力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.40,0:11:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我没想到今天会这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.40,0:11:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.73,0:11:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里湿了吧?让我摸摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.86,0:11:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在这里啦\N真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被发现的\N可以的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.46,0:12:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫出来会被听到哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.86,0:12:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.60,0:12:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经超湿了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.26,0:12:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心，不会有事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.60,0:12:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托，不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会叫出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.53,0:12:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这么了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.20,0:13:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这么了，来含吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?来嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.73,0:13:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.40,0:13:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这么了，来含嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.00,0:13:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦\N来含嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.66,0:13:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪?\N等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.33,0:13:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之只要安静就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.93,0:13:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.53,0:13:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的啦\N怎么可能没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静就没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.33,0:13:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.46,0:14:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是睡在哪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.66,0:14:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寝室吗?那只要不大声叫\N就不会被现咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来继续刚刚的吗?\N不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.46,0:14:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会忍不住的啦\N那就来看看能到什么程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么啊?\N其实你干劲十足吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这种的啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.66,0:14:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来让我好好舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.13,0:14:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.73,0:15:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像平时一样用口水吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.06,0:15:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好色啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.13,0:15:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.86,0:15:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超赞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.40,0:15:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是千沙的味道啊，真美味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.20,0:15:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很躁动了吧?\N等等啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.86,0:15:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要做吗?\N要做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.73,0:16:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来用这里了，不行大声叫哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.26,0:16:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在好湿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.86,0:16:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.20,0:16:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.13,0:16:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想舔你的小穴想得受不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.33,0:16:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也喜欢被舔吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好张开让我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.93,0:16:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两手掰开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.66,0:17:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要都掰开哦\N这样子可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.93,0:17:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，掰好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.13,0:17:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泛着光啊，真赞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.60,0:17:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来舔这里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.26,0:17:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想用小穴吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.80,0:17:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦\N不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.93,0:17:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老公在睡啊\N你可是这么湿了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.93,0:17:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己听听这个声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.20,0:18:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真下流的声音啊\N会受不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真下流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.33,0:18:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了吧？\N不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.80,0:18:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求我像平时一样舔穴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.93,0:18:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，会叫出来的\N只要忍耐就好了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.00,0:18:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.13,0:18:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微...\N稍微什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.60,0:18:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔我吧\N想要我舔啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就稍微舔一下咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.33,0:19:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里外来同时用哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.40,0:19:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.40,0:19:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.33,0:20:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿哒哒呢\N今天回去了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.66,0:20:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊...\N那是因为...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.66,0:20:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都只有你自己爽...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.60,0:20:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是老公吧?真的假的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.33,0:20:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗?\N觉得身体舒服多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.20,0:20:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚实在是不舒服呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.66,0:20:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.40,0:20:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚在做什么?\N在看手机啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看手机哦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.73,0:21:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用再休息吗?\N还是去躺着比较好吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.73,0:21:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但觉得睡不着啊\N是啊，可是你身体不好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.73,0:21:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子不太好吧?\N我看一下报纸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.00,0:21:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看报纸啊?\N一直躺很无聊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.13,0:22:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退烧了吗?\N倒是没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.46,0:22:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也没有想睡了\N还是躺着好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.73,0:22:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的，一会就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.20,0:22:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是担心啊，去休息吧\N没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.80,0:23:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么不想休息?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.66,0:23:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.86,0:23:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去睡吗?\N再一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.66,0:23:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.53,0:23:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要让感冒快点好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.46,0:23:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.46,0:24:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N突然好想咳嗽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.33,0:24:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我们传染了？\N也许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.60,0:24:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不要太靠近我好了\N是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.20,0:24:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吗?我还是不要离你太近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.13,0:24:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是被我们传染了\N是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.86,0:24:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去睡了\N要记得穿暖一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.40,0:24:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.53,0:24:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.86,0:24:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到你竟然忍得住啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.60,0:25:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很兴奋吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.13,0:25:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有兴奋吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.73,0:25:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等\N把屁股翘好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.53,0:25:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说今天不要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:50.13,0:25:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴在收缩了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:54.66,0:25:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被老公看着所以兴奋了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:59.46,0:26:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.86,0:26:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁眼在抽动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:28.53,0:26:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舌头可以进去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:40.66,0:26:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚抬起来哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:46.66,0:26:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.33,0:27:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么容易去啊，兴奋了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:19.46,0:27:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的，不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:24.93,0:27:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来换我爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:30.53,0:27:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来舔吧，你老公不会来的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:40.66,0:27:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:48.26,0:27:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来舔奶头吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:02.66,0:28:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公在反而让你兴奋吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:06.53,0:28:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:18.40,0:28:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:27.60,0:28:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用老二的前端吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:40.26,0:28:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞\N来含吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:58.80,0:29:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢这一根\N喜欢我的啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:11.86,0:29:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:26.26,0:29:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:34.80,0:29:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好，过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:09.46,0:30:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:09.86,0:30:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:14.93,0:30:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:21.20,0:30:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:37.73,0:30:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:49.33,0:30:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想插了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:55.06,0:30:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:00.53,0:31:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我老公在休息啊\N他在睡了，没事的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:07.73,0:31:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不知道啊，等我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:12.66,0:31:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的，要快回来啊\N都这个样子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:22.40,0:31:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太多心了啦\N但有可能会醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:21.73,0:32:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流好多汗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:28.13,0:34:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫出来被发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:03.33,0:35:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的水声啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:09.33,0:35:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要安静哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:25.46,0:35:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠近一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:33.60,0:35:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:16.13,0:37:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到忍住了啊\N明明都流那么多汁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:24.26,0:37:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都湿答答了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:27.86,0:37:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来含我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:39.20,0:37:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点会醒的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:58.93,0:38:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要含深一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:30.13,0:38:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:26.40,0:39:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来发出声音吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:43.73,0:39:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来，要出发吸吮的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:18.40,0:40:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托，不要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:23.86,0:40:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:30.40,0:40:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们继续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:47.73,0:40:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:52.40,0:40:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡成那样子，没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:02.40,0:41:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那下流的舌头\N真是让人受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:09.86,0:41:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要玩吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:21.06,0:41:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:38.66,0:41:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直湿答答呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:43.33,0:41:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没这么过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:47.46,0:41:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在老公面前嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:06.00,0:42:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一会再来玩哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:12.00,0:42:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:35.20,0:42:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把脚张开吧\N这么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:41.33,0:42:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:49.73,0:42:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看着我舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:03.60,0:43:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:20.93,0:43:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔了哪啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:24.26,0:43:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阴核
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:28.00,0:43:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你最爱的阴核唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:31.46,0:43:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天实在太赞了，不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:43.86,0:43:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真赞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:54.13,0:43:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好激烈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:57.46,0:44:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老公不在，这就好好地去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:12.13,0:44:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那里，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:23.33,0:44:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:46.00,0:44:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么湿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:52.40,0:44:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的嘴也是穴汁，帮我弄干净吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:58.80,0:45:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要全都舔掉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:05.20,0:45:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舌头再伸出来一点\N要好好舔干净哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:22.00,0:45:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来帮我含吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:30.66,0:45:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超赞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:49.86,0:45:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来舔着老二前端吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:57.33,0:45:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用口水吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:05.33,0:46:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞\N真行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:16.26,0:46:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来插入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:21.06,0:46:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无套插入哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:25.06,0:46:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要啊\N那说是哪里想要什么插啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:30.80,0:46:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪里想要无套老二插啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:38.00,0:46:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里想要无套老二插入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:46.13,0:46:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:49.46,0:46:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来全都进去哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:52.93,0:46:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都看光了，好紧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:06.80,0:47:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:25.73,0:47:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太大声会被听到的\N抱歉，但是好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:31.33,0:47:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:52.13,0:47:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:56.40,0:47:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很赞吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:27.86,0:48:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么吗?\N是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:31.86,0:48:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己好好掰开来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:44.80,0:48:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:46.93,0:48:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:07.06,0:49:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流出好多下流汁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:10.26,0:49:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:31.86,0:49:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:37.20,0:49:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:48.53,0:49:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天实在很不妙啊\N很有感吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:56.26,0:49:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不正常了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:18.80,0:50:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:23.86,0:50:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天最下流呢\N那是因为...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:33.20,0:50:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:10.80,0:51:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么拍打很爽吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:35.73,0:51:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:57.60,0:51:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:02.80,0:52:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?\N好爽，受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:07.20,0:52:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:29.33,0:52:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插得好深啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:34.66,0:52:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:41.20,0:52:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:05.86,0:53:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:39.33,0:53:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:46.66,0:53:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:49.73,0:53:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么用，真下流啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:56.66,0:53:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:07.46,0:54:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，插到子宫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:16.13,0:54:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真淫荡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:22.26,0:54:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:33.20,0:54:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:39.60,0:54:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:45.06,0:54:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:48.66,0:54:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想去吧?\N等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:57.06,0:54:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是有够湿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:01.33,0:55:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天实在是不正常了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:09.73,0:55:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来多玩一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:55.73,0:55:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好激烈\N太赞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:06.00,0:56:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:24.13,0:56:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:28.66,0:56:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是湿哒哒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:42.66,0:56:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很赞吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:46.13,0:56:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:50.93,0:56:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:58.66,0:57:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:13.20,0:57:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，我受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:19.73,0:57:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:30.80,0:57:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:32.93,0:57:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也到极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:56.93,0:57:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:06.00,0:58:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:10.93,0:58:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可以中出吗?\N可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:16.80,0:58:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:20.40,0:58:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了\N把热精射给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:27.33,0:58:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，脑袋一片空白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:34.93,0:58:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:39.60,0:58:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:47.86,0:58:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都射出来了，超爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:12.40,0:59:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:15.20,0:59:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:20.13,0:59:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，好热啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:30.26,0:59:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:45.06,0:59:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好浓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:48.53,0:59:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我下次再来咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:53.20,0:59:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次老公确实上大夜时\N再和我连络吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:57.86,1:00:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:19.46,1:00:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（佳奈，27岁，结婚第3年）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:26.80,1:01:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漏水了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:31.33,1:01:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得找修水电的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:45.60,1:01:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噫?怎么没接呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:55.73,1:02:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道这附近的便利屋\N会不会修水管呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:11.06,1:02:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，这边是有委托过的森泽家
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:18.40,1:02:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次真是谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:21.20,1:02:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我家漏水了\N有办法修理吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:32.26,1:02:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:35.60,1:02:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以，想要今天修理
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:39.20,1:02:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是在哪呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:43.73,1:02:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分后就会到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:46.80,1:02:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了，那可以过来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:52.80,1:02:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:58.66,1:03:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:04.26,1:03:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是哪里漏的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:10.80,1:03:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是够湿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:29.60,1:03:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:31.60,1:03:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在这里\N是厨房下方啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:38.26,1:03:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是这里漏出来的\N原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:45.86,1:03:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不进去看不知道呢\N是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:52.00,1:03:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里头的东西得清出来呢\N麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:04.53,1:04:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就先放上去咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:54.80,1:04:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吗？\N还可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:04.00,1:05:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放哪里好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:17.73,1:05:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我来帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:23.06,1:05:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗?\N没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:26.13,1:05:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思\N放上去就好了嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:30.80,1:05:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思\N那全部放上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:35.60,1:05:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N这个放一旁就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:43.06,1:05:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪边漏出来的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:47.06,1:05:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是很里头呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:05.20,1:06:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看一下\N不知道是哪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:12.40,1:06:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:16.26,1:06:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是排水管的某一处
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:23.60,1:06:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子啊\N总是要清过再封补才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:33.06,1:06:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子啊，可是费用不少吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:38.80,1:06:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都找我们很多次了\N可以优待的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:44.39,1:06:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:53.20,1:06:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是这里吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:00.80,1:07:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要摸一下才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:17.60,1:07:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看吧\N麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:30.53,1:07:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,状况不太好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:34.39,1:07:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带来的工具，要修好很勉强呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:50.26,1:07:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要修要花多久时间?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:54.53,1:08:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是第一次看到的\N也许要一小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:02.26,1:08:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:04.66,1:08:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去打扫，修好就叫我一声
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:11.20,1:08:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了，那就开始修咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:15.06,1:08:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:30.40,1:08:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修漏水好像要一段时间呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:02.40,1:09:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:43.86,1:09:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?\N要修很久？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:46.93,1:09:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:50.53,1:09:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点躁了呢\N你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:59.60,1:10:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在啊没事的，他在修理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:07.60,1:10:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很专心的，没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:10.40,1:10:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被发现的\N没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:17.33,1:10:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦\N来摸一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:24.13,1:10:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啦\N可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:34.66,1:10:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\N没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:34.93,1:10:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\N没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:38.26,1:10:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来摸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:54.26,1:10:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦\N没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:58.26,1:10:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:04.53,1:11:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:04.66,1:11:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:04.80,1:11:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:05.33,1:11:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:05.46,1:11:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:06.53,1:11:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:12.40,1:11:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都硬了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:27.73,1:11:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了\N真的要?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:32.26,1:11:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:43.06,1:11:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:45.60,1:11:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:56.26,1:11:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:37.33,1:12:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:42.66,1:12:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太太现在分不开身\N怎么了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:46.80,1:12:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思，我想要插电
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:54.00,1:12:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以用一下吗?\N没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:58.40,1:12:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:03.06,1:13:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思，还要花点时间\N还要大约多久?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:08.26,1:13:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少要十多分以上\N是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:13.73,1:13:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太去哪了呢? \N去其它房间打扫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:20.00,1:13:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子啊，我准备一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:13.73,1:14:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点复杂呢\N这样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:19.60,1:14:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有三个管路\N那就不容易了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:39.06,1:15:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要用零件了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:09.86,1:16:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下去来好好用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:34.00,1:16:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:38.66,1:16:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一下就射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:50.53,1:16:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也来舔我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:55.46,1:16:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先继续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:38.13,1:17:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也来舔我的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:43.20,1:17:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先继续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:46.80,1:17:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会要哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:04.53,1:18:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:07.33,1:18:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这附近吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:14.40,1:18:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了，舌头出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:33.73,1:18:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了，射出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:38.80,1:18:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:41.33,1:18:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射出来了呢\N是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:44.66,1:18:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快拿面纸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:04.66,1:19:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多呢，还好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:08.93,1:19:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽\N是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:12.66,1:19:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽就射出来了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:17.46,1:21:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便利屋的，如何了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:24.00,1:21:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要再一会呢\N这样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:29.60,1:21:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该一会就会好的\N我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:17.33,1:23:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?\N看到一只小蟑螂
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:21.60,1:23:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蟑螂?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:24.80,1:23:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:28.80,1:23:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太，没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:32.13,1:23:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跌了一下\N这样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:44.26,1:23:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太没穿内裤?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:52.66,1:23:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:00.40,1:24:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它撕破吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:07.33,1:24:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:07.46,1:24:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:07.60,1:24:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:07.73,1:24:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:07.86,1:24:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:08.00,1:24:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:08.13,1:24:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:08.40,1:24:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:10.80,1:24:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:17.33,1:24:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:26.80,1:24:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老公没问题吗?\N没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:38.40,1:24:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以撕破吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:41.06,1:24:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点撕破吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:53.20,1:24:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:06.93,1:25:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都看光了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:15.60,1:25:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想摸吧?\N可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:19.20,1:25:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:23.73,1:25:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:27.86,1:25:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好湿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:32.80,1:25:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老公呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:41.46,1:25:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也已经累到睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:46.53,1:25:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:50.00,1:25:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以做这重事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:56.53,1:26:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是今天突然找你来的服务哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:09.06,1:26:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好紧张啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:13.73,1:26:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想看这里吗?\N想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:20.93,1:26:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:40.13,1:26:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:48.66,1:26:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光看就好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:04.53,1:27:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:08.80,1:27:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来多摸点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:14.53,1:27:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太的身材真赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:24.66,1:27:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:27.86,1:27:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:38.66,1:27:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:48.13,1:27:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:01.46,1:28:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞\N这里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:07.46,1:28:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:20.80,1:28:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:00.40,1:29:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:05.33,1:29:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:45.06,1:29:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:01.46,1:30:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:06.40,1:30:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美的小穴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:15.73,1:30:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多用一点\N多用一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:20.26,1:30:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子吗?\N对
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:53.60,1:30:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:00.26,1:31:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:06.00,1:31:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:31.33,1:31:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:38.26,1:31:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以起来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:14.66,1:32:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都变成这样子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:19.20,1:32:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，太太这么湿呢\N因为好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:30.26,1:32:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得好湿了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:33.06,1:32:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来弄干净哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:59.86,1:33:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:08.00,1:33:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太实在是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:39.86,1:33:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从后面来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:56.40,1:33:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:06.26,1:34:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:45.86,1:34:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:20.66,1:35:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太去了吗?\N实在是太爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:46.00,1:35:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以用便利屋的这里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:53.86,1:35:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以这样子吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:01.06,1:36:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解开了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:13.73,1:36:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，竟然连那里都用
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:24.66,1:36:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来看了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:32.80,1:36:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思，又成样子子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:38.00,1:36:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:04.53,1:37:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:28.26,1:37:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:45.33,1:37:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么大声会听到的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:11.86,1:38:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:26.53,1:38:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要这个了呢\N可以插入吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:33.86,1:38:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:38.13,1:38:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗?\N没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:46.53,1:38:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:48.13,1:38:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点插进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:52.40,1:38:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:07.33,1:39:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子可以吗?\N别管了，继续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:13.20,1:39:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:16.26,1:39:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在夹好紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:40.93,1:39:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太，那么大声，会被听到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:27.73,1:40:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?\N好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:38.80,1:40:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被听到的，忍住
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:54.13,1:40:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快叫出来了吧?\N别管了，继续插吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:59.73,1:41:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:10.66,1:41:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:21.46,1:41:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的会被察觉的\N别管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:45.86,1:41:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:51.60,1:41:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这么下去，真的会被发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:04.53,1:42:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公，寝室的冷气\N好像也有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:16.13,1:42:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找便利屋的一起看看，如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:24.26,1:42:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就麻烦一下咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:34.66,1:42:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去寝室吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:42.80,1:42:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先穿一下裤子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:03.06,1:43:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了\N麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:07.86,1:43:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这机型很旧了呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:18.93,1:43:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:48.66,1:43:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:20.53,1:44:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这台要多花点时间，没问题吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:31.73,1:44:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要很花时间啊?\N因为机型很旧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:00.66,1:45:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多点时间也没差\N能帮我们看看吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:10.40,1:45:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就检查一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:21.73,1:45:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修理时会有灰尘，\N把门关起来比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:50.13,1:45:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:27.46,1:46:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多插一点\N多一点吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:46.80,1:46:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽\N是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:03.60,1:47:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:28.66,1:47:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫这么大声没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:33.20,1:47:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正在睡了，又关起门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:42.00,1:47:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多插一点，不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:49.60,1:47:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了，不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:55.86,1:48:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:26.66,1:48:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗?\N就是那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:42.80,1:48:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:47.73,1:48:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:58.40,1:49:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸我的奶头
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:07.73,1:49:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夹好紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:11.60,1:49:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个小穴真会夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:16.40,1:49:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:27.60,1:49:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:32.00,1:49:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插得好深啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:36.53,1:49:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:49.46,1:49:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:54.26,1:49:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:23.20,1:50:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个实在好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:33.73,1:50:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:35.73,1:50:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在摩擦小穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:38.40,1:50:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:44.93,1:50:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插得好里头呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:49.33,1:50:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:19.46,1:51:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:24.53,1:51:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从下面多插一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:37.06,1:51:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:40.26,1:51:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，再多一点\N这么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:43.73,1:51:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:46.26,1:51:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样，不行，再多插一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:55.73,1:51:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:11.33,1:52:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了\N好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:20.53,1:52:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:26.93,1:52:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在好硬\N是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:31.20,1:52:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在好爽\N和老公的比呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:39.33,1:52:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的老二比较大\N比较硬，好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:52.13,1:52:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那里，多插一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:00.66,1:53:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:43.46,1:53:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在好赞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:48.80,1:53:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么插着小穴好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:56.80,1:53:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:03.86,1:54:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:10.40,1:54:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:19.73,1:54:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:37.60,1:54:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:50.40,1:54:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:54.00,1:54:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽，不行，要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:59.20,1:55:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多插一点\N好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:02.80,1:55:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:18.26,1:55:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢被舔吗?\N喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:35.33,1:55:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来多一点\N好爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:39.86,1:55:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:51.73,1:55:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:54.66,1:55:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了\N可以哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:58.66,1:56:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:10.53,1:56:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:19.73,1:56:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太去了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:42.00,1:56:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很赞吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:54.66,1:56:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞\N这么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:58.13,1:56:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多插一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:07.20,1:57:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:25.46,1:57:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:56.13,1:57:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那里..
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:26.00,1:58:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:29.86,1:58:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太，我受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:36.13,1:58:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了吗?\N可以射吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:42.26,1:58:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接射出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:45.73,1:58:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中出吗?\N嗯，中出吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:50.13,1:58:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:53.60,1:58:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的，中出吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:59.73,1:59:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就中出咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:06.93,1:59:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要才射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:51.06,2:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太太，我可以没修好就回去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:05.46,2:00:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水管就找水电的来修吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:10.40,2:00:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不继续了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:15.33,2:00:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:16.53,2:00:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
